## Plots
 
```{r  plot}


g<-ggplot(df, aes(x=POWER_E, y=COOLANT_OUTLET_T_C, color=COOLANT)) +  
  geom_point(aes(shape=SPECTRUM))+
  facet_wrap(~COUNTRY)+
  theme_light()  

ggplotly(g)
